title: Domestic passenger vehicle wholesales dip 1% to 3.56 lk units in Sep: SIAM
description: The Society of Indian Automobile Manufacturers reported a 1% decline in passenger vehicle wholesales in September 2023, while two-wheeler sales rose 16% YoY to 20,25,993 units and three-wheeler wholesales 7% YoY to 79,683 units.
